original: Bengtsson, Adèle Daga Ann-Marie, tandläkare. Vara, f. 25/10/10 i Gbg av Edvard Gustafsson o. Adèle Sandström. G. 38 m. tandl. Bengt Bengtsson. Barn: Rolf f. 39, Ingela 42, Marianne 45. — Stud:ex. v. Sigrid Ru-debecks gymn. i Gbg 30, tandl :kand. 33, tandläkare 36. Vik. i bl, a. Höganäs, Knivsta, Töreboda, Katrineholm o. Fjällbacka, praktik i Vara sed. 38.
translated: Bengtsson, Adèle Daga Ann-Marie, dentist. Born on 25/10/10 in Gothenburg to Edvard Gustafsson and Adèle Sandström. Married in 1938 to dentist Bengt Bengtsson. They have three children: Rolf, born in 1939, Ingela in 1942, and Marianne in 1945. Adèle completed her secondary education at Sigrid Ru-debeck's gymnasium in Gothenburg in 1930. She received her dental degree in 1933 and became a licensed dentist in 1936. She worked in various locations including Höganäs, Knivsta, Töreboda, Katrineholm, and Fjällbacka. She started her own practice in Vara in 1938 and continues to work there.
